00:21:40.700 --> 00:21:41.910
Ah ouais ? Où ça ?

00:21:42.060 --> 00:21:43.570
Hé, les gars...

00:21:45.410 --> 00:21:46.450
Bellamy !

00:21:47.320 --> 00:21:49.110
C'est quoi, cette histoire d'or ?

00:21:50.250 --> 00:21:52.630
Ce fameux cricket...

